name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'KulimPark-ExtraLight', Everything looks good.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Kulim Park' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight' = NID 1 'Kulim Park ExtraLight'.

Kulim Park ExtraLight Italic (KulimPark-ExtraLightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'KulimPark-ExtraLightItalic', Everything looks good.

Kulim Park ExtraLight Italic (KulimPark-ExtraLightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Kulim Park' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight Italic' = NID 1 'Kulim Park ExtraLight' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'KulimPark-Light', Everything looks good.

Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. You may not copy or distribute this software. If you have any questions concerning your rights you should review the license agreement you received with the software. Kulim Park Light Regular (KulimPark-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Kulim Park' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Kulim Park Light'.

Kulim Park Light Italic (KulimPark-LightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Kulim Park' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light Italic' = NID 1 'Kulim Park Light' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Kulim Park Regular (KulimPark-Regular.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '

NID 6 is 'KulimPark-Regular', Everything looks good.

Kulim Park SemiBold Regular (KulimPark-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'KulimPark-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. You may not copy or distribute this software. If you have any questions concerning your rights you should review the license agreement you received with the software. Kulim Park SemiBold Regular (KulimPark-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Kulim Park' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold' = NID 1 'Kulim Park SemiBold'.

Kulim Park SemiBold Italic (KulimPark-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Kulim Park' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold Italic' = NID 1 'Kulim Park SemiBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

underlinePosition should be a negative and underlineThickness not 0 or negative.

underlinePosition is '-100'.
underlineThicknes is '50'.

Pass
